ate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-exit-strategy-from-gaza-that-hasnt-been-adopted/0000018b-8c23-d46b-a18f-8cfb36d20000</guid></item><item><title>这些是加沙贾巴利亚难民营遭到轰炸后被救出的儿童</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/these-are-the-children-extracted-after-the-bombardment-of-gazas-jabalya-refugee-camp/0000018b-8c23-d46b-a18f-8cfb57690000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 01:44:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/these-are-the-children-extracted-after-the-bombardment-of-gazas-jabalya-refugee-camp/0000018b-8c23-d46b-a18f-8cfb57690000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长：立即向巴勒斯坦当局转移资金；哈马斯指挥官在以色列国防军空袭中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-live/11-israeli-soldiers-killed-as-idf-expands-gaza-ground-operation/0000018b-8925-d055-afbf-bba702e90000</link><description>自加沙地面行动开始以来，已有 16 名以色列士兵丧生 ■ 也门胡塞武装发动远程导弹和无人机袭击后，以色列军舰部署在红海作为增援部队 ■ 以色列空袭杀死了哈马斯贾巴利亚旅指挥官和 10 月 7 日大屠杀中的一名领导人易卜拉欣·比亚里 (Ibrahim Biari) ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部：8,000 多名巴勒斯坦人被杀 ■ 240 名人质在加沙被扣押，40 人仍然失踪 ■ 至少 1,300 名平民和士兵在哈马斯大屠杀中丧生</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 00:24:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-live/11-israeli-soldiers-killed-as-idf-expands-gaza-ground-operation/0000018b-8925-d055-afbf-bba702e90000</guid></item><item><title>为了应对日益增长的压力，哥伦比亚大学和宾夕法尼亚大学宣布打击反犹太主义的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/responding-to-growing-pressure-columbia-and-penn-announce-plans-to-combat-antisemitism/0000018b-8cb7-db7e-af9b-eff725b10000</link><description>自10月7日哈马斯入侵以色列以来，两所大学一直面临来自犹太教师、学生和校友的压力，要求解决犹太学生的安全问题</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 22:34:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/responding-to-growing-pressure-columbia-and-penn-announce-plans-to-combat-antisemitism/0000018b-8cb7-db7e-af9b-eff725b10000</guid></item><item><title>对于以色列人来说，加沙长期血腥战争的现实正在击中要害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/for-israelis-the-reality-of-a-long-bloody-war-in-gaza-is-hitting-home/0000018b-8bf6-db7e-af9b-ebf78b290000</link><description>加沙战争不会是冲向明确胜利线的冲刺，而是一场漫长而混乱的马拉松。以色列公众希望跑步者的脚不会像不久前那样陷入难处理的泥浆中</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 19:25:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/for-israelis-the-reality-of-a-long-bloody-war-in-gaza-is-hitting-home/0000018b-8bf6-db7e-af9b-ebf78b290000</guid></item><item><title>美国认为巴勒斯坦权力机构是加沙问题的可能解决方案，但以色列正在努力削弱它</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sees-palestinian-authority-as-possible-solution-in-gaza-as-israel-works-to-weaken-it/0000018b-8b8a-db7e-af9b-ebcb50e30000</link><description>尽管由总统马哈茂德·阿巴斯领导的陷入困境的约旦河西岸机构得到了拜登政府的支持，但极右翼的以色列部长们却试图扣留对该机构的资助</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 17:12:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sees-palestinian-authority-as-possible-solution-in-gaza-as-israel-works-to-weaken-it/0000018b-8b8a-db7e-af9b-ebcb50e30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会极右翼成员兹维·苏科特将担任约旦河西岸小组委员会主席</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-knesset-member-zvi-sukkot-to-head-subcommittee-on-the-west-bank/0000018b-8b93-db71-a7df-ffdfd1ea0000</link><description>住棚节年轻时是宗教犹太复国主义党的成员，曾因涉嫌参与约旦河西岸的犹太极端主义活动而成为辛贝特安全部门的目标</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 16:20:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-knesset-member-zvi-sukkot-to-head-subcommittee-on-the-west-bank/0000018b-8b93-db71-a7df-ffdfd1ea0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯官员：我们将重复10月7日的袭击，直到以色列被歼灭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/hamas-official-we-will-repeat-october-7-attacks-until-israel-is-annihilated/0000018b-8b9d-db7e-af9b-ebdfbee90000</link><description>哈马斯官员加齐·哈马德告诉黎巴嫩电视台，以色列的存在是所有暴力和痛苦的根源</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 16:10:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/hamas-official-we-will-repeat-october-7-attacks-until-israel-is-annihilated/0000018b-8b9d-db7e-af9b-ebdfbee90000</guid></item></channel></rss>